      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Newly trained dogs heading for prison wings to sniff out illegal drugs
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Over 170 specially trained sniffer dogs are heading to prisons across England and Wales as part of the government’s comprehensive plan to crack down on violence and crime behind bars.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 11 November 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
        <dl data-module="track-click">
